; PolyField Track — Wind-only LSS (Raw mode)
; Use this as a SECOND scoreboard entry in FinishLynx alongside polyfield.lss.
; Set Running Time to Raw. Points to the same IP and port as the main entry.
; Raw mode is required for ;;Wind to fire.

; PolyField Track — FinishLynx LSS Script v2.0
; Outputs pipe-delimited text via UDP to PolyField Track on port 5001.
; Defaults: 9600,8,N,1

; --- Clock & Timing State ---

;;TimeArmed

;;TimeRunning

;;TimeUpdate

;;TimeStopped

;;TimePaused

;;TimeOfDay

; --- Wind (Raw mode — fires on every beam break, filter "no data" in receiver) ---

;;Wind
\12\01wind:%s\r\n

; --- Start List (sent when event is loaded, before gun) ---

;;StartListHeader

;;StartList

; --- Started (sent once gun fires — keeps start list visible during race) ---

;;StartedHeader

;;Started

; --- Results (Live) — sent each time results are updated ---

;;ResultsHeader

;;Results

;;ResultsTrailer